# platformio.ini (Nano)

Use `nanoatmega328` / `atmelavr`. Strict `lib_deps`:

- adafruit/RTClib
- pololu/VL53L0X
- adafruit/Adafruit SSD1306 + Adafruit GFX Library
- adafruit/Adafruit MPU6050 + Unified Sensor
- adafruit/Adafruit NeoPixel

Copy from [claude_pathfinder/.context/template-platformio.ini](claude_pathfinder/.context/template-platformio.ini).
